thers, FIFA and UEFA).  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jun 2022) 4aSport /Recht. 4aSportorganisationen /Recht. 7aLAW / General.2bisacsh  aSports (law).  asports organizations.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Law - 2000 - 2014z9783110636208oZDB-23-GLA08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2007z9783110277135oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET RECHTSWISSENSCHAFTEN 2007z9783110276978oZDB-23-DGC0 cprintz978389949383240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311091450440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110914504423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110914504/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGCb2007  aZDB-23-DGGb2007  aZDB-23-GLAc2000d2014